data.text:
Adolf Josef Ferdinand Galland is a male German-speaking gerenuk aviator and general in the Zootopia Defence Force Air Force. Adolf along with his brothers Fritz, Wilhelm and Paul were all brought up in a loving but strict family of Huguenot ancestry.
